summary: A test suite dedicated to validating the Vision Transformer Masked AutoEncoder (ViTMAE) implementation, covering configuration correctness, deterministic inference, pretraining behavior, handling of alternative input embeddings, model output consistency, and proper serialization/deserialization including fast initialization pathways.
business_intent: Guarantee the reliability and correctness of the ViTMAE model for production use, enabling confident deployment, maintenance, and integration within computer vision pipelines.
